---
title: Hoisin Grilled Chicken with Sesame Veggies and Buttered Rice
description: The grill makes this fuss-free summer recipe a breeze! Sweet and sticky hoisin-glazed chicken tenders pair up with sesame soy veggies for a scrumptious dinner to enjoy outdoors with your crew.
